Financial Aid Electronic Award Letter Instructions







You will receive an email message from the Office of Student Financial Aid notifying you of when your financial aid award letter is available for viewing.
In order to view your award letter, you must activate your Netid and password.


View Electronic Award Letter

Activate your NetId and password.
Log into my.UIC.edu.
In the first column on the Welcome page, click on Financial Aid Status Menu
Click on Award Letter.








